data.description: A recently updated 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with fresh paint inside & out, new floors, new carpet, new fixtures, ceiling fans, all matte black hardware, new tubs, toilets & more!  The eat-in kitchen is fully equipped with new shaker style cabinets, granite countertops & new stainless steel appliances!  You'll notice the relaxing wood burning fireplace with butcher block mantle in the great room.  The converted garage can make a 2nd huge master suite (4th bedroom) or entertainment area.  This home is equipped with all vinyl windows and a separate laundry room.  Outside there is ample parking in front yard and a huge fully fenced in, private, backyard.  Located in the desired Dorchester District II schools this makes for the perfect, updated & turn key home.  Book your showing today!
